import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';

function RegisterForm() {
    return (
      <Form style={
        {margin: 40}
      }>
        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="RegisterFrom.ControlInput1">
        <Form.Label htmlFor="email">Email</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
            id = "email"
            type = "text"
            placeholder="Email ID"
            required
        />
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="RegisterFrom.ControlInput2">
        <Form.Label htmlFor="username">Username</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
            id="username"
            type= "text"
            placeholder="Username"
            required
        />
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="RegisterFrom.ControlInput3">
        <Form.Label htmlFor="password">Password</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control
            id = "password"
            type= "password"
            placeholder="Password"
            required
        />
        <Form.Text id="passwordHelpBlock" muted>
        Your password must be 8-20 characters long.
        </Form.Text>
        </Form.Group>

        <Button variant="primary" className="mb-3" type="submit">Register</Button>
      </Form>
    );
}

export default RegisterForm;
